videos.description: Alabama turns defense into offense when Kira Lewis Jr. steals the ball and gets it to Alex Reese, who knocks down a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Reese sinks 3 for Alabama

videos.description: Skylar Mays dribbles around the arc and gets open for a 3-pointer for LSU.
videos.headline: Mays knocks down wide-open 3

videos.description: Trendon Watford loses control of the ball, and Kira Lewis Jr. steals it and takes it to the other end for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Alabama's Lewis steals, makes layup) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Alabama's Lewis steals, makes layup

videos.description: LSU's Skylar Mays steals the ball and takes it to the other end for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mays hangs on rim after slam) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Mays hangs on rim after slam

videos.description: After Marlon Taylor blocks Kira Lewis Jr.'s layup, Alex Reese gets the rebound and sinks a 3-pointer, giving Alabama an 85-80 lead that they wouldn't give up.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Reese knocks down big 3 for Alabama) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Reese knocks down big 3 for Alabama
